    General Stores in Lower Parel, Mumbai

    In India, general stores or mom-n-pop shops are generally referred to as 'kiranas'. It is a form of traditional retail where it offers a wide range of products. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Mentioned above is a vast list of General Stores in Lower Parel, Mumbai.
